{"tid":2408660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"秘魯外長被揭發秘密優先接種中國疫苗　引咎辭職","createTime":"2021-02-15T07:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T07:48:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3e938580cc30c0d0da74dadd2c9b332b79646ef5","tid":2408660,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:08:37.000Z","msg":"秘魯外長阿斯特特被揭發在全國接種疫苗計劃展開前，秘密優先接種中國國藥集團的疫苗，引咎辭職。<br />\n<br />\n阿斯特特在社交網站貼文說，知道自己犯了嚴重錯誤，所以決定不接種第二劑疫苗，她已向總統薩加斯蒂請辭。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，因貪腐被國會罷免下台的前總統比斯卡拉承認，他和太太在去年10月已提早接種國藥疫苗。衛生部長馬塞蒂被指隱瞞有關信息，提出辭職，總統薩加斯蒂已經接納。<br />\n<br />\n秘魯政府上月初宣布，與國藥集團達成協議，購買國藥的疫苗，上星期二展開接種計劃，並優先為前線醫護人員接種。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575748-20210215.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575748-20210215.htm&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4ecg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=75b6d1ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575748-20210215.htm&h=39ed6550\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575748-20210215.htm</a>"},{"pid":"db58bd50da2c38bfd3a2f87d07cbb345cbbda0a5","tid":2408660,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ed8a849d1afa0fec33c86a57cd3a72b5b4730f","tid":2408660,"uid":113000,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:09:51.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8126e79254414d84acad36c042d71b204310b3","tid":2408660,"uid":76804,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:10:27.000Z","msg":"想行先一步姐<br />\n咁都要辭職既話<br />\n林鄭要辭100次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h